---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Azure Cloud Portfolio">

<section id="home" class="min-h-screen flex flex-col justify-center items-center">
  <h1 class="text-5xl text-[#64ffda]">Azure Cloud Architect</h1>
  <p class="mt-4 text-xl">MSP · Automation · AI Integration Specialist</p>
</section>

<section id="about" class="min-h-screen p-10">
  <h2 class="text-3xl text-[#64ffda] mb-4">About Me</h2>
  <p>11년차 클라우드 엔지니어로 Azure MSP, 클라우드 이관, 자동화 시스템 구축을 전문으로 하고 있습니다.</p>
</section>

<section id="skills" class="min-h-screen p-10">
  <h2 class="text-3xl text-[#64ffda] mb-4">Skills</h2>
  <div class="space-y-4">
    <div>Azure Compute (VM, AppService, Function) <div class="w-full bg-gray-700 h-3 rounded"><div class="bg-[#64ffda] h-3 rounded" style="width:90%"></div></div></div>
    <div>AKS / Kubernetes <div class="w-full bg-gray-700 h-3 rounded"><div class="bg-[#64ffda] h-3 rounded" style="width:85%"></div></div></div>
    <div>Azure Networking (VNET/VPN) <div class="w-full bg-gray-700 h-3 rounded"><div class="bg-[#64ffda] h-3 rounded" style="width:80%"></div></div></div>
    <div>Azure Security / Governance <div class="w-full bg-gray-700 h-3 rounded"><div class="bg-[#64ffda] h-3 rounded" style="width:75%"></div></div></div>
    <div>IaC: Terraform / Bicep <div class="w-full bg-gray-700 h-3 rounded"><div class="bg-[#64ffda] h-3 rounded" style="width:70%"></div></div></div>
    <div>Monitoring & Automation <div class="w-full bg-gray-700 h-3 rounded"><div class="bg-[#64ffda] h-3 rounded" style="width:80%"></div></div></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="portfolio" class="min-h-screen p-10">
  <h2 class="text-3xl text-[#64ffda] mb-4">Portfolio</h2>
  <ul class="list-disc ml-5 space-y-2">
    <li>Azure 기반 MSP 통합 운영 자동화 시스템 구축</li>
    <li>Terraform 기반 Azure Resource 자동 생성 시스템</li>
    <li>Azure Monitor 기반 인프라 장애/성능 리포트 자동화</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<section id="contact" class="min-h-screen p-10">
  <h2 class="text-3xl text-[#64ffda] mb-4">Contact</h2>
  <p>Email: your_email@example.com</p>
  <p>LinkedIn: <a href="#" class="text-[#64ffda] underline">your_linkedin</a></p>
</section>

</Layout>
